=Description=

"Dr. Rey Junco - Associate Professor and the Director of Disability Services in the Department of Academic Development and Counseling at Lock Haven University - is at the helm of one of the first experimental studies to assess whether first-year college students’ use of Twitter affects student engagement and success. Here he talks about some of his early findings."


